Package me.pagekite.glen3b.library.bukkit.scoreboard

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractBoardManager
    Represents an abstract scoreboard manager, which implements a skeletal framework for scoreboards.
    ScoreboardEntry
    Represents an entry in a "scoreless" scoreboard.
    ScoreboardInformation
    Represents information about a soon-to-be-created scoreboard.
    ScorelessBoardManager
    Represents a sidebar scoreboard manager which does not utilize Minecraft's score feature except for ordering.
    ScorelessBoardManager.Spacers Deprecated
    This class will be replaced with a more vertasile system of dealing with duplicate values, rendering it pointless as ScorelessBoardManager.SPACER_ENTRY can be used.
